Mission.Title: C7M11sanitized final
Mission.Comments:
CAMPAIGN 7: NEOFEUDAL SANDLORDS MISSION 11: VERY TURKISH TIME IN MY LIFE
Last week, we scammed a turkish supremacist militia out of 40,000lbs of gold bullion, part of which we used to bribe our casualty insurance agent to keep our blanket policy in place.
We're still barracks'd in house with Benzos forces in Turkiye and the base is buzzing with logistics units staging for a major ground operation. We don't know much about what to expect or what his ultimate objective is, just that Benzos is planning to put our company out in front of all of it.
He's has forward positioned his forces on the far side of the mountain range we ran last mission and they will be pushing SW towards Hatay and ultimately to their objective in Antakya.
We don't know what's there, but it must be valuable because the AI has mustered a large combined arms assault brigade that will be moving NE up the valley to meet our employer's forces. They will be overwhelmed without our help.
Company Objective: Provide CAS to the Benzos ground mercs moving SW through the valley.
Company Secondary Objective: Hold the surrounding airspace and clear SAM threats.
Weather: Clear, 23degC, light wind Mission Local Time: ~1900 - last light
